Hi! Im Steph. I am a freelance journalist making a career change into tech. I am learing how to use data science to take logical steps in my life. 

Data Science is the confidence behind statements. I can sit here and tell you that "a" is better than "b" from here until tommorow. However, unless I can back those
words, they mean nothing. Data Science is the statistics that allows me to say "a" is more... than "b" and here is why. 
